description:
It has been a while since the last gameplay video on my channel, but I decided to bring the series back with Minecraft: Bedrock Edition. In this video, I also speak and react to events while playing this game, which is a new concept for this series. I'm playing the game in survival mode, where you have to collect resources to survive in the Minecraft world.

► About the audio issues
I forgot my microphone to stereo mode (even tough it records in mono), so I set the whole video to mono, which is better than having audio on only one side. The noise is caused by the fact that the microphone audio level was really low (I wasn't using a headset, so I had the microphone sitting about 20 centimeters away from me) and I had to increase the volume at points. Another thing contributing to the noise was the fact that I didn't even have noise cancellation turned on while recording.

I was able to reduce some noise by recording noise with the same microphone and using that as the noise profile in Audacity, then merging it with the video using ffmpeg. I hope you forgive me, since this is the first actual gameplay video I've made with real-time commentary.

► About the game
Minecraft Bedrock is a newer multi-platform version of Minecraft written in C++ . Read more: https://minecraft.fandom.com/wiki/Bedrock_Edition
Platform version: Minecraft for Windows
World seed: Windows RT
